 ```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="56ef9-162">ただし、これらの特殊文字をエスケープで、次のコンス トラクターで作成、<xref:System.Net.Cookie>に追加できる、<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer>インスタンス。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="56ef9-162">However, the following constructor with these special characters escaped will create a <xref:System.Net.Cookie> that can be added to a <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instance:</span></span>  
 
 ```csharp
 System.Net.Cookie cookie = new System.Net.Cookie("contoso", "\"123,456\"", "", "https://contoso.com");
 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="56ef9-163">コンマ文字は、同じ行に個別の cookie を区切る区切り記号として使用されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="56ef9-163">The comma character is used as a delimiter between separate cookies on the same line.</span></span>
